- see http://code.google.com/p/bigbluebutton

To install polling module:
-Open ~/dev/bigbluebutton/bigbluebutton-client/src/conf/config.xml, and add
		<module name="PollingModule" url="PollingModule.swf?v=3809" 
			uri="rtmp://<SERVER IP>/bigbluebutton" 
			host="http://<SERVER IP>" 
			dependsOn="ViewersModule"
		/>
-Go to ~/dev/bigbluebutton and execute install-web-polling.sh
